I"<p>rvm,git,rbenv,gem 得都是学习<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">rails</code>中常用的工具，这些最常用命令行语句做个记录备查。</p>

<h3 id="using-rvm">using rvm</h3>
<hr />

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>/bin/bash --login

rvm gemset use bloggem

rvm list

rvm use 2.3.3

rvm gemset list

rvm gemset create  railsapp

rvm use 2.3.3@railsapp

rvm gemset delete railsapp
</code></pre></div></div>

